owledge-act-upon\/","url_meta":{"origin":41914,"position":0},"title":"Ibn Salam on &#8216;Ilm: Masters of knowledge act upon what they know","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ubaydullah ibn Umar reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said to Abdullah ibn Salam, \u201cWho are the masters of knowledge?\u201d Abdullah said, \u201cThose who act upon what they know.\u201d Umar said, \u201cWhat nullifies knowledge in the hearts of men?\u201d Abdullah said, \u201cGreed.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304 595\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18222,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/20\/seeking-knowledge-jihad\/","url_meta":{"origin":41914,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Seeking knowledge is jihad in way of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 20, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever goes out seeking knowledge is in the way of Allah until he returns.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2647 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33999,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/02\/16\/hasan-ilm-two-types\/","url_meta":{"origin":41914,"position":2},"title":"Hasan on \u2018Ilm: Knowledge is two types, beneficial or hypocritical","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 16, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Hisham reported: Al-Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cKnowledge is two types: Knowledge in the heart is that which benefits. Knowledge on the tongue will be an indictment against the son of Adam.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304 376 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0647\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0627\u0645 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13002,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/20\/whoever-conceals-knowledge\/","url_meta":{"origin":41914,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Secrets: Whoever hides knowledge will be punished","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is asked about knowledge and he conceals it, Allah will clothe him with a bridle of fire on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2649 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42296,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/10\/18\/knowledge-better-worship\/","url_meta":{"origin":41914,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Knowledge: Learning better than voluntary worship","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 18, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah ibn al-Yaman reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe virtue of knowledge is better than the virtue of worship, and the best of your religion is conscientious piety.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 3960 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24198,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/12\/18\/ilm-scholars-inheritors-prophets\/","url_meta":{"origin":41914,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Knowledge: Scholars are successors of prophets","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 18, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe scholars are the successors of the prophets. Verily, the prophets do not pass on gold and silver coins, but rather they only impart knowledge.\u201d Source: Musnad al-Bazza\u0304r 10\/68 Grade: Salih (good) according to Al-Bazza\u0304r \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u06